RACE.RACE_TEXT: Don C. McNeill S. REMINGTON PARK RACE 7 1M Dirt CR: 71. Stakes Purse 50000. FOR TWO YEAR OLDS. ACCREDITED OKLAHOMA FOALS. No nomination fee. $600 to pass the entry box at the usual time of entry. Starters to pay an additional $500 with $50,000 Guaranteed by Remington Park and an additional $25,000 Plus from the Oklahoma Bred Fund . Supplementary nominations may be made at time of entry for a fee of $2,200, which qualifies to start. Weights; 121 lbs. Non-winners of a stakes allowed 2 lbs. Maidens allowed 4 lbs. High weights preferred. Then Preference to Highest Lifetime Earnings of Horses with Equal Weights. Lifetime Earnings will be determined according to statistics provided by Equibase.
